OL,3,CShakespeare's Globe theatre defends
OL,4,Ccasting non-disabled actor as Richard
OL,5,CIII
OL,7,Fby , Content Editor
OL,9,FShakespeare's Globe theatre has
OL,10,Fdefended casting a non-disabled actor
OL,11,Fas Richard III in this summer's
OL,12,Fproduction following backlash.
OL,14,FThe theatre has faced criticism after
OL,15,Fit announced its artistic director
OL,16,FMichelle Terry would play the
OL,17,Fvillainous king, who has historically
OL,18,Fbeen portrayed with a physical
OL,19,Fdisability.
