OL,7,FAn open letter by campaign group ,
OL,8,Fsigned by more than 100 disabled
OL,9,Ftheatre professionals, said it was
OL,10,F"outraged and disappointed" by the
OL,11,Fdecision and called for an "immediate
OL,12,Frecast" of the role.
OL,14,FIt went on: "Richard III is an iconic
OL,15,Fdisabled character. Perhaps the most
OL,16,Ffamous disabled character in the
OL,17,FBritish canon.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/9
