OL,7,F"To see The Globe announce this
OL,8,Fcasting within this production is
OL,9,Fshocking... The production cannot be
OL,10,Fsuccessfully performed with a non-
OL,11,Fphysically disabled actor at the helm,
OL,12,Fsteering the complex and vitally
OL,13,Fimportant narrative.
