OL,5,CIII
OL,7,FBrittanie Pallett, an actor with a
OL,8,Fdisability, wrote online: "Why is an
OL,9,Fartistic director of any theatre,
OL,10,Fhiring themselves to play the lead
OL,11,Fwhen its not their casting or lived
OL,12,Fexperience?"
OL,14,F"Before anyone says it doesn't matter.
OL,15,FEvery time this happens more harm than
OL,16,Fgood is done to disabled communities
OL,17,Fthrough misrepresentation."
OL,19,FIn 2023, Bridgerton actor Adoja Andoh
OL,20,Fplayed Richard III in a production at
OL,21,FLiverpool's Playhouse.
