OL,8,Fpeople are "demonised" for what they
OL,9,Flook like.
OL,11,FThe skeleton of Richard III was in
OL,12,F2012.
OL,14,FHe has historically been portrayed as
OL,15,Fhaving one shoulder larger than the
OL,16,Fother, but tests revealed he suffered
OL,17,Ffrom scoliosis or curvature of the
OL,18,Fspine.
